 {"id":"bd-4bit6.3","title":"Resolve legacy e2compr algorithm parity gaps","description":"Mock/stub sweep finding from crates/ffs-core/src/lib.rs: e2compr decompression/compression reports algorithms other than gzip/LZO/none as not implemented (lzv1, lzrw3a, bzip2 legacy formats). Decide whether these are in FrankenFS scope. If in scope, implement readers/writers with fixtures and conformance tests; if out of scope, make the exclusion explicit in PLAN_TO_PORT_FRANKENFS_TO_RUST.md and FEATURE_PARITY.md and keep the runtime error precise. Acceptance: no hidden algorithm gap remains; fixtures cover every supported method and every explicit exclusion; targeted core tests plus workspace check/clippy pass.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-27T05:22:04.597214726Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-27T05:22:04.597214726Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2compr","ext4","stub-sweep"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-4bit6.3","depends_on_id":"bd-4bit6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-27T05:22:04.597214726Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
